data.description: This charming Cape Style house features a classic design exuding timeless allure. Inside, the main floor comprises a living room, large eat in kitchen three cozy bedrooms offer comfortable living spaces. Practical amenities, such as ample closet space plus there is a finished basement with a kitchenette area to ensure functionality This house is ideally suited for small families, couples, or individuals seeking a manageable and inviting living space, epitomizing the perfect blend of classic architectural charm and practical comfort. Walk to park for easy conveniences
